overview.en: HE-1 is the stablecoin of Hacker Federation. Hacker Federation, initiated by practitioners of traditional financial institutions and top encryption technicians in the blockchain industry, was an ecological alliance focusing on digital asset investment and financial management, established through the Decentralized Autonomous Organization (DAO). Its purpose is to create an open, shared, secure and highly encrypted digital economy for global users. Hacker Federation's digital asset investment and financing platform is committed to creating the world's top encryption digital asset circulation platform for users, which is easy to use, fast, flexible, convenient, safe, stable income and high return on investment.
overview.zh: HE-1是Hacker Federation的稳定币。Hacker Federation骇客联盟是由传统金融机构从业者与区块链行业顶级加密技术人员发起，通过去中心化自治式组织（DAO）创立的一个专注于数字资产投资理财的生态联盟。联盟的宗旨是为全球用户打造一个价值开放、共享、安全、高度加密的数字经济体。骇客联盟数字资产投资理财平台致力为用户打造易用快捷，灵活方便，高度安全，稳固收益投资回报率高的全球顶尖加密数字资产流通平台。
